findStrings.find: def pytest_collection_modifyitems( self, items: List[nodes.Item] ) -> Generator[None, None, None]: res = yield if self.active: new_items: Dict[str, nodes.Item] = {} other_items: Dict[str, nodes.Item] = {} for item in items: if item.nodeid not in self.cached_nodeids: new_items[item.nodeid] = item else: other_items[item.nodeid] = item items[:] = self._get_increasing_order( new_items.values() ) + self._get_increasing_order(other_items.values()) self.cached_nodeids.update(new_items) else: self.cached_nodeids.update(item.nodeid for item in items) return res
